features: Great for Adults and Teens (may fit some larger children)

description: Stand tall with this lovely headpiece which truly reflects the spirit of the statue of Liberty. This striking headpiece features rubber material with stiffened peaks and an elastic closure (for a more comfortable fit). Perfect for 4th of July and other summer holidays, parades, theatrical productions, cosplay, The Purge, school plays and projects and more.
